				<span>Overview of Signature Account</span>
			</h2>
			<div class="content-section">
				<p class="silver">Beyond Banking</p>
				<h2>A Signature Account deserves nothing but the</h2>
				<h2>best from the best in the business</h2>
				<p>SVC Bank is hououred to be your Banking Partner, and is pleased to welcome you to your Signature Account - a premium service offering,specfically designed to cater to your elite banking needs. We take pride in providing top quality Personalised Banking Service and are sure, your every need will be met with swift and expert support,always. Let your time be reserved for just your passion, because we are taking over your banking needs for you.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="row-section">
				<div class="sg-col-4">
					<div class="img-section">
						<img src="{{ module_path[0] }}/images/dedicated_relationship_thumb.jpg" alt="image"/>
					</div>
					<div class="content-section">
						<h2 class="ov-title">Dedicated Relationship Manager</h2>
						<p>Banking just got simpler, with the appointment of a Dedicated Manager for you who will be exclusively handling your banking needs, as per your instrutions</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sg-col-4">
					<div class="img-section">
						<img src="{{ module_path[0] }}/images/service_benefit_thumb.jpg" alt="image"/>
					</div>

					<div class="content-section">
						<h2 class="ov-title">Serve Benefits</h2>
						<p>Anytime/anywhere banking through complimentary SVC Debit Card with enhanced limits and host of offers & privileges</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sg-col-4">
					<div class="img-section">
						<img src="{{ module_path[0] }}/images/offers_rewards_thumb.jpg" alt="image"/>
					</div>

					<div class="content-section">
						<h2 class="ov-title">Offers and Rewards Program</h2>
						<p>As your Banking Partner, we pay close attention to your need.That's why our dedicated loyalty progran offers you attractive, intelligent rewards on every transaction made.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
    <div class="sva-section">
      <div class="img-section">
        <img src="{{ module_path[0] }}/images/kids_with_coins.jpg" alt="signature-logo"/>
      </div>
      <div class="content-section">
        <div class="content">
          <p class="silver">Special Value Additions</p>
          <h2>Insurance, Concierge Services and Airport Lounges. May your every journey be safe and relaxing</h2>

          <p class="sva-ul-title">Insurance Benefits</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Complimentary Personal Accidental Death Cover worth INR 10 Lakhs**</li>
            <li>Additional, complimentary personal Accidental Death cover worth INR 2 Lakhs*</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="sva-ul-title">Travel Benefits</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Complimentary Personal Accidental Death Cover worth INR 10 Lakhs**</li>
            <li>Additional, complimentary personal Accidental Death cover worth INR 2 Lakhs*</li>
          </ul>

