        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sh-section">
      <p class="silver">Signature Highlights</p>
      <h2 class="sh-title">Welcome to a world of exclusive banking benefits, customised to suit your preferences.</h2>
      <div class="row-section">
        <div class="sh-col-2">
          <div class="content">
            <ul>
              <li>Complimentary RuPay Platinum Debit Card with host of offers and privileges</li>
              <li>Access to Digital Banking suite form the comfort of your home</li>
              <li>Enhanced Debit Card cash withdrawal/ Ecom/POS limit of INR 50,000 per day</li>
              <li>Unlimited Free ATM Transactions (On SVC Bank as well as other Bank ATMs)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-col-2">
        <div class="content">
          <ul>
            <li>Free Demat Account opening with Zero Anuual Maintenance Charges for the first year</li>
            <li>Unlimited free cheque leaves and DD/PO</li>
