            <li>Preferential ROI and discounts on Retail Loan Processing Fees</li>
          </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="sh-tc">*Terms & condition apply</p>
    </div>

    <div class="shq-section">
      <div class="l-content">
        <h1>Still Have Query ?</h1>
        <div>
          <a id="faqBtn" class="btn-query">Click Query</a><p>to view detailed FAQs</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="R-content">
        <img src="{{ module_path[0] }}/images/help_image.png" alt="signature-logo"/>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sh-section">
      <p class="silver">Eligibility</p>
      <h2 class="sh-title">Welcome to a world of exclusive banking benefits, customised to suit your preferences.</h2>
      <div class="row-section">
        <div class="sh-col-2">
          <div class="content">
            <ul>
              <li>Eligible to all saving account with Privilege Relationship with SVC Bank</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-col-2">
        <div class="content">
          <ul>
            <li>Minimum average quarterly balance of Rs 2 Lakh*</li>
          </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="sh-tc">*Terms & condition apply</p>
    </div>

    <div class="sh-approve-section" id="upgrade-section">
      <h1>Move into a world of exclusive privileges at no extra cost. Upgrade to SVC Bank Signature Account now!</h1>
        <div class="sha-button">
          <a href="#" class="btn-info">Need more information</a>
          <a class="btn-continue" id="myBtn">Yes, continue</a>
        </div>
		<div class="error-msg" style="color:red;text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;"></div>
    </div>
</div>
{% include '@d8campaign/campaign-footer.html.twig' %}
</div>
<!-- Let's output the three variables passed to this template -->

<div id="myModal" class="modal">
<div class="modal-content">
<span class="close">&times;</span>
<div class="otp-section">
	<div class="otp-img"><img src="{{ module_path[0] }}/images/password_icon.png" alt="otp-image"/></div>
	<h1>OTP <span style="color:red">*</span> </h1>
	<p>Kindly Enter the One Time Password (OTP) sent to your registered mobile number.</p>
	<form id="otp-form">
		<div class="otp-input">
			<input type="text" name="ot1" id="ot1" maxlength="1" required>
			<input type="text" name="ot2" id="ot2" maxlength="1" required>
			<input type="text" name="ot3" id="ot3" maxlength="1" required>
			<input type="text" name="ot4" id="ot4" maxlength="1" required>
			<input type="text" name="ot5" id="ot5" maxlength="1" required>
			<input type="text" name="ot6" id="ot6" maxlength="1" required>
		</div>
		<div class="error-msg-otp"></div>
		<input type="hidden" value="signature" name="cvalue" id="cvalue">
		<input type="submit" value="submit" class="otp-submit">
		<input type="button" value="Resend SMS" class="otp-resend">
	</form>
</div>
</div>
</div>


<div id="faqModal" class="modal">
<div class="modal-content">
<span class="closefaq">&times;</span>
<div class="FAQ-section">
	<h1>FAQs</h1>
	<div class="main">
		<!-- faq block start -->
		<div class="faq-wrapper">
			<div class="heading open">What is the AQB requirement of Signature Account?<span class="arrow"></span></div>
			<div class="content" style="display:block">AQB requirement of SB Classic account is INR 200000</div>
		</div>
		<!-- faq block end -->
		<!-- faq block start -->
		<div class="faq-wrapper">
			<div class="heading head-back">What are the charges if Average Quarterly Balance (AQB) is not maintained?<span class="arrow"></span></div>
			<div class="content">There are no charges for non maintenance of minimum balance. (However account will be downgraded to normal account on non maintenance of requisite balances)</div>
		</div>
		<!-- faq block end -->
		<!-- faq block start -->
		<div class="faq-wrapper">
			<div class="heading head-back">What are the Insurance benefits associated with Signature Account?<span class="arrow"></span></div>
			<div class="content">Every primary holder of a Classic Savings account receives a complementary Accidental Death Insurance Cover of Rs. 10 Lakhs, sponsored by SVC Bank and underwritten by Aditya Birla Health insurance Co. Ltd.</div>
		</div>
		<!-- faq block end -->
		<!-- faq block start -->
		<div class="faq-wrapper">
			<div class="heading head-back">What are the Debit Card features associated with Signature Account?<span class="arrow"></span></div>
			<div class="content">
				<ul>
					<li>Signature Account is entitled to receive a complimentary Rupay Platinum Debit Card with no Annual Maintenance Charges.</li>
					<li>Rupay Platinum Debit Card comes with an Personal Accidental Death Insurance Cover of INR 2,00,000*</li>
					<li>This Card offers customers complimentary access to airport lounges*</li>
				</ul>
				<span>* Terms and Conditions Apply</span>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- faq block end -->
	</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

